{
  "texts": [
    "• Cash Flow -Cash flow statements show the business's incoming and outgoing funds for a particular duration.",
    "It shows how the cash flow movement affects the balance sheet within the same duration.",
    "In a nutshell, cash flow statements reflect the business's financial health.",
    "• Income Statement-The income statement is one of the most important parts of the financial statement, especially for investors looking deeply into the income to make necessary judgment about the business.",
    "An income statement is the profit and loss statement within a particular time duration."
  ]
}